_sText:
• Br Steezus

Alpha version 2

A Battle Royale map made originally for a hunger games server but would suit being on a minigame server.

Inspired by Electrified by Mike Danielsson

All players start in a box at the outskirts of the map. As the gas closes in on the middle it forces players to go to the middle of the map and fight. Last one standing wins.
